These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
2 different pets are kept: rat, mouse
There are 2 different favourite colors: black, azure
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: rock, salsa
House: gothic-revival, cottage
1. the gothic-revival house is not to the right of the person who likes azure##8
2. the person who likes azure is somewhere to the left of the fan of rock##5
3. the owner of the rat is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Pet      | mouse     | rat      |
| Color          | azure | black    |
| Music-Genre         | salsa   | rock |
| House   | gothic-revival  | cottage      |

