.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, cat
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: zinnia, aconite
There 2 different types of food: garlic, cherry
House: cottage, futuristic
1. the owner of the cat is on the far right##1
2. the person who growszinnia is somewhere to the left of the person eating garlic##5
3. the person eating cherry is not to the right of the person eating garlic##8
4. the cottage house is not the person who growsaconite##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Pet    | chinchilla        | cat    |
| Flower       | zinnia         | aconite |
| Food         | cherry | garlic   |
| House   | cottage               | futuristic  |

