There 2 different types of food: pumpkin, watermelon
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, bike
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the person driving the bike##8
3. the person eating pumpkin is somewhere to the left of the person who likes purple##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Color   | emerald       | purple |
| Food   | pumpkin       | watermelon    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | milk |
| Transport           | ship        | bike   |

