City: prague, venice
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, april
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, vegafina
1. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to venice##5
2. the person watching comedy movies is not to the left of the vegafina-smoker##8
3. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre         | western | comedy  |
| City           | venice  | prague |
| Birthday   | april | july   |
| Cigar     | vegafina   | ritmeester |

